Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:18.17,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}{\c&D9D9D9}起きてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:19.25,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}{\c&999999}イヤだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.50,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&000000\4c&000000}{\c&D9D9D9}{\bord2.5}起きろってんでしょうが
